    "Name": "Orestes",
    "Details": "Designed in 3032, the Orestes is a cheap to produce support VTOL, developed to diversify the Taurian Defense Forces VTOL roster with a home grown design. A 20 ton VTOL, the Orestes is powered by a 105 rated fusion engine and armed with paired Machine Guns and LRM-5s.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 10/15 hexes / 300/450 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        75     10\n<b>Left</b>          60     10\n<b>Right</b>        60     10\n<b>Rear</b>         50     10\n\n<b>Total</b>      255     50</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Missile Jammer</color>",
